quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,"akhbr -ayha alrswl- eibadi 'aniy 'ana alghafur lilmuminin altaybyn, alrahim bhm, wa'ana eadhabi hu aleadhab almwlm almwje lighayr altaybyn. wakhbrhm -ayha alrswl- ean duyuf 'iibrahim min almalayikat aladhin bshsharwh balwld, wbhlak qawm lwt"
  15,51,"akhbr -ayha alrswl- eibadi 'aniy 'ana alghafur lilmuminin altaybyn, alrahim bhm, wa'ana eadhabi hu aleadhab almwlm almwje lighayr altaybyn. wakhbrhm -ayha alrswl- ean duyuf 'iibrahim min almalayikat aladhin bshsharwh balwld, wbhlak qawm lwt"
  15,52,"hyn dakhaluu ealayh fqalu: slamana; fard ealayhim alslam, thuma qddam lahum altaeam falam yaklu, qal: 'iinaa minkum fzewn"
  15,53,"qalt almalayikat lh: la tfze 'inna jina nubashiruk bwld kthyr aleilm baldyn, hu 'ishaq"
  15,54,"qal 'iibrahim mtejbana: abshshartmwny balwld, wa'ana kabir wzwjty kdhlk, fabi'ayi aejwbt tbshshirwnny?"
  15,55,"qalu: bshsharnak bialhaqi aldhy aelmana bih allh, fala takun min alyaysyn 'ana yualid lk"
  15,56,"qal: la yyys min rahmat rabih 'iilaa alkhatiuwn almnsrfwn ean tariq alhq. qal: fama al'amr alkhatir aldhy jitum min 'ajalih -ayha almrslwn- min eind allh?"
  15,57,"qal: la yyys min rahmat rabih 'iilaa alkhatiuwn almnsrfwn ean tariq alhq. qal: fama al'amr alkhatir aldhy jitum min 'ajalih -ayha almrslwn- min eind allh?"
  15,58,"qalu: 'iina allah 'arsalna l'ihlak qawm lut almushrikin aldaaliyn 'iilaa lwtana wa'ahlah almuminin bh, falan nhlkhm wsnnjyhm ajmeyn, lkn zawjatih alkafrt qadayna bi'amr allah b'ihlakha mae albaqin fi aledhab"
  15,59,"qalu: 'iina allah 'arsalna l'ihlak qawm lut almushrikin aldaaliyn 'iilaa lwtana wa'ahlah almuminin bh, falan nhlkhm wsnnjyhm ajmeyn, lkn zawjatih alkafrt qadayna bi'amr allah b'ihlakha mae albaqin fi aledhab"
  15,60,"qalu: 'iina allah 'arsalna l'ihlak qawm lut almushrikin aldaaliyn 'iilaa lwtana wa'ahlah almuminin bh, falan nhlkhm wsnnjyhm ajmeyn, lkn zawjatih alkafrt qadayna bi'amr allah b'ihlakha mae albaqin fi aledhab"
  15,61,"flma wasal almalayikat almursalun 'iilaa lwt, qal lhm: 'iinakum qawm ghyr merwfyn ly"
  15,62,"flma wasal almalayikat almursalun 'iilaa lwt, qal lhm: 'iinakum qawm ghyr merwfyn ly"
  15,63,"qalu: la takhaf, f'inna jina bialeadhab aldhy kan yashuku fih qawmak wala yusaddiqwn, wjynak bialhaqi min eind allh, wa'iinaa lsadqwn, fakhruj min baynihim wmek 'ahlak almwmnwn, baed murur juz' min allyl, wsr 'ant wra'hm; lialaa ytkhlf minhum ahd fynalh aledhab, wahdharuu 'ana yaltafit minkum ahd, wasreu 'iilaa hayth 'amarakum allh; litakunuu fi makan amyn"
  15,64,"qalu: la takhaf, f'inna jina bialeadhab aldhy kan yashuku fih qawmak wala yusaddiqwn, wjynak bialhaqi min eind allh, wa'iinaa lsadqwn, fakhruj min baynihim wmek 'ahlak almwmnwn, baed murur juz' min allyl, wsr 'ant wra'hm; lialaa ytkhlf minhum ahd fynalh aledhab, wahdharuu 'ana yaltafit minkum ahd, wasreu 'iilaa hayth 'amarakum allh; litakunuu fi makan amyn"
  15,65,"qalu: la takhaf, f'inna jina bialeadhab aldhy kan yashuku fih qawmak wala yusaddiqwn, wjynak bialhaqi min eind allh, wa'iinaa lsadqwn, fakhruj min baynihim wmek 'ahlak almwmnwn, baed murur juz' min allyl, wsr 'ant wra'hm; lialaa ytkhlf minhum ahd fynalh aledhab, wahdharuu 'ana yaltafit minkum ahd, wasreu 'iilaa hayth 'amarakum allh; litakunuu fi makan amyn"
  15,66,wawhyna 'iilaa lut 'ana qawmak mstasalwn balhlak ean akhiruhum eind tulue alsbh
  15,67,"wja' 'ahl madinat lut 'iilaa lut hin ealimuu biman eindah min aldywf, wahum farihun yastabshirun bdywfh; lyakhdhwhm wyfelu bihim alfahsht"
  15,68,"qal lahum lwt: 'iina hwla' dayfi wahum fi hmayty fala tfdhwny, wkhafu eiqab allh, wala tterdu lhm, ftwqewny fi aldhuli walhwan b'iydhaykm ldywfy"
  15,69,"qal lahum lwt: 'iina hwla' dayfi wahum fi hmayty fala tfdhwny, wkhafu eiqab allh, wala tterdu lhm, ftwqewny fi aldhuli walhwan b'iydhaykm ldywfy"
  15,70,"qal qwmh: 'awalam nanhak 'ana tdyif 'ahadana min alealmyn; lanna nurid minhum alfahsh?"
  15,71,"qal lut lhm: hwla' nisawukum banati ftzwwajwhn 'iin kuntum turidun qada' wtrkm, wsmahn bnath; li'ana nabiin al'umat bmnzlt alab lhm, wala tafealuu ma hrram allah ealaykum min 'ityan alrjal"
  15,72,"yqsm alkhaliq biman yasha' wabima ysha', 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, waqad 'aqsam allah taealaa bihayat muhamad salaa allah ealayh wasalam tshryfana lh. 'iina qawm lut fi ghaflat shadidat yataradadun wytmadwn, hataa hllat bihim saeiqat aleadhab waqt shrwq alshms"
  15,73,"yqsm alkhaliq biman yasha' wabima ysha', 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, waqad 'aqsam allah taealaa bihayat muhamad salaa allah ealayh wasalam tshryfana lh. 'iina qawm lut fi ghaflat shadidat yataradadun wytmadwn, hataa hllat bihim saeiqat aleadhab waqt shrwq alshms"
  15,74,"fqlbna qurahm fajaealna ealiaha saflha, wa'amtarna ealayhim hijaratan min tin mtslb mtyn"
  15,75,"'iina fima 'asabahum laezat lilnaazirin almetbryn, wa'iin qrahm lafi tariq thabt yaraha almsafrwn almarrun bha. 'iina fi 'ihlakna lahum ladlaltan byintan llmsdqyn aleamilin bshre allh"
  15,76,"'in fima 'asabahum laezat lilnaazirin almetbryn, wa'iin qrahm lafi tariq thabt yaraha almsafrwn almarrun bha. 'iina fi 'ihlakna lahum ladlaltan byintan llmsdqyn aleamilin bshre allh"
  15,77,"'in fima 'asabahum laezat lilnaazirin almetbryn, wa'iin qrahm lafi tariq thabt yaraha almsafrwn almarrun bha. 'iina fi 'ihlakna lahum ladlaltan byintan llmsdqyn aleamilin bshre allh"
  15,78,"wqd kan 'ashab almadinat almltft alshajar -whm qawm sheyb- zalimin lanfshm lkfrhm biallah wrswlhm alkrym, fantaqamna minhum balrjft waeadhab yawm alzlt, wa'iin masakin qawm lut wsheyb lafi tariq wadih ymrr bihima alnaas fi safarihim fyetbrwn"
  15,79,"wqd kan 'ashab almadinat almltft alshajar -whm qawm sheyb- zalimin lanfshm lkfrhm biallah wrswlhm alkrym, fantaqamna minhum balrjft waeadhab yawm alzlt, wa'iin masakin qawm lut wsheyb lafi tariq wadih ymrr bihima alnaas fi safarihim fyetbrwn"
  15,80,"wlqd kdhdhab sukkan \"wady alhijr\" salhana ealayh alslam, wahum thamud fakanuu bdhlk mukadhibin likuli almrslyn; li'ana min kdhdhab nbyana faqad kdhdhab al'anbia' klhm; li'anahum ealaa din wahd"
  15,81,"watyna qawm salih ayatina aldalt ealaa sihat ma ja'ahum bih salih min alhq, wamin jmltha alnaqt, falam yetbru bha, wakanuu eanha mbtedyn merdyn"
  15,82,"wkanu yanhitun aljbal, fytkhdhwn minha bywtana, wahum aminun min 'an tasqut ealayhim 'aw tkhrb"
  15,83,"fakhdhthm saeiqat aleadhab waqt alsabah mbkryn, fama dafe eanhum edhab allah alamwal walhswn fi aljbal, wala ma 'uetwh min quat wjah"
  15,84,"fakhdhthm saeiqat aleadhab waqt alsabah mbkryn, fama dafe eanhum edhab allah alamwal walhswn fi aljbal, wala ma 'uetwh min quat wjah"
  15,85,"wama khlaqna alsmwat wal'ard wama baynahuma 'iilaa bialhaqi daltyn ealaa kamal khalqhma waqtdarh, wa'anah aldhy la tnbghy alebadt 'iilaa lah wahdah la sharik lh. wa'iina alsaaeat alty taqum fiha alqiamat latiat laa mhalt; ltwffa kulu nafs bima emlt, faef -ayha alrswl- ean almshrkyn, wasfah eanhum watajawuz eamaa yfelwnh"
  15,86,"'inn rabak hu alkhlaaq likuli shy', alealim bh, fala yejzh shay' fi al'ard wala fi alsma', wala yakhfaa elyh"
  15,87,"wlqd ataynak -ayha alnby- fatht alqran, wahi sbe ayat tkrr fi kl slat, watynak alquran alezym"
  15,88,"la tanzur beynyk wttmnn ma mattaena bih asnafana min alkufaar min mutae aldnya, wala tahzan ealaa kfrhm, wtwadae lilmuminin biallah wrswlh"
  15,89,"wql: 'iiniy 'ana almndhr almwddih lamaa yahtadi bih alnaas 'iilaa al'iiman biallah rabi alealmyn, wmndhrkm 'an yusibakum aledhab, kama 'anzalah allah ealaa aladhin qssamu alqran, faminuu bbedh, wakafaruu bbedh alakhar min alyhwd walnsara wghyrhm"
  15,90,"wql: 'iiniy 'ana almndhr almwddih lamaa yahtadi bih alnaas 'iilaa al'iiman biallah rabi alealmyn, wmndhrkm 'an yusibakum aledhab, kama 'anzalah allah ealaa aladhin qssamu alqran, faminuu bbedh, wakafaruu bbedh alakhar min alyhwd walnsara wghyrhm"
  15,91,"whm aladhin jaealuu alquran aqsamana wajza', faminhum man yqwl: shr, waminhum man yaqul kahant, waminhum man yaqul ghyr dhlk, ysrrifwnh bhsb ahwayhm; liasuduu alnaas ean alhda"
  15,92,"fwrbk lnhasbnnahm yawm alqiamat walanajzianahum ajmeyn, ean tqsymhm llqran baftra'athm, wthryfh wtbdylh, waghayr dhlk mimaa kanuu yemlwnh min eibadat alawthan, wamin almeasy walatham. wafi hdha tarhib wzjr lahum min al'iqamt ealaa hadhih alafeal alqbyht"
  15,93,"fawarabik lnhasbnnahm yawm alqiamat walanajzianahum ajmeyn, ean tqsymhm llqran baftra'athm, wthryfh wtbdylh, waghayr dhlk mimaa kanuu yemlwnh min eibadat alawthan, wamin almeasy walatham. wafi hdha tarhib wzjr lahum min al'iqamt ealaa hadhih alafeal alqbyht"
  15,94,"fajhr bidaewat alhaqu alty amrk allah bha, wala tbal balmshrkyn, faqad brrak allah mmma yqwlwn"
  15,95,"'inna kafaynak almustahziiyn alsaakhirin min zueama' qrysh, aladhin atakhadhuu shrykana mae allah min al'awthan wghyrha, fasawf yaelamun eaqibat eamalahum fi aldunya walakhrt"
  15,96,"'inna kafaynak almustahziiyn alsaakhirin min zueama' qrysh, aladhin atakhadhuu shrykana mae allah min al'awthan wghyrha, fasawf yaelamun eaqibat eamalahum fi aldunya walakhrt"
  15,97,wlqd naelam banqbad sadruk -ayha alrswl-; bsbb ma yaquluh almushrikun fyk wafi dewtk
  15,98,"fafze 'iilaa rabik eind dayq sdrk, wsabbih bihamdih shakrana lah mthnya elyh, wakun min almsllin lilah aleabidin lh, fa'iina dhlk ykfyk ma ahmmak"
  15,99,"wastmirr fi eibadat rabik mdt hyatk hataa yatiak alyqyn, wahu almwt. wamtthl rasul allah salaa allah ealayh wasalam 'amr rbh, falam yzl daybana fi eibadat allh, hataa atah alyaqin min rbh"